      • checkFormCreateParameters

        protected void checkFormCreateParameters(String presentationId,
                             String formTypeId,
                             String itemDefId)
        Check to see that all form creation parameters are set and valid. Throws IllegalArgumentException on any errors.
        Parameters:
        presentationId - Presentation from which the form is being edited
        formTypeId - Form type ID for the form to be edited
        itemDefId - Presentation Item Definition ID of the "slot" for the item

      • checkFormEditParameters

        protected void checkFormEditParameters(String presentationId,
                           String formTypeId,
                           String formId,
                           String itemDefId)
        Check to see that all form editing parameters are set and valid. Throws IllegalArgumentException on any errors.
        Parameters:
        presentationId - Presentation from which the form is being edited
        formTypeId - Form type ID for the form to be edited
        formId - The specific artifact ID to edit
        itemDefId - Presentation Item Definition ID of the "slot" for the item
